”Tell me about the company”

skdetail:

Invocation Name: capital innovators
des:
Capital Innovators provides startups with the resources and connections they need to get to the next level and beyond. 

Use this skill to:
- Get information about Capital Innovators
- Get information about Accelerator Program
- Learn about the Team
- Learn about the Capital Innovators Accelerator Program
- What are some of the perks? 
- Who are the mentors, sponsors, and partners?
- Get Contact Information
- Get leadership team bios
- Learn about the Ameren Accelerator
- Learn what companies are part of the new class 
- Detailed list of commands available by saying Help

For more information visit http://www.CapitalInnovators.com
